title: Illusion_Suite_-_Clips_from_The_First_Adventure_(Live_at_Gamla_O
description:
Illusion Suite - Clips from The First Adventure (Live at Gamla, Oslo 23.06.2006)

This video shows Illusion Suit&#039;s veri first live gig!
For those who haven&#039;t heard Illusion Suite, they are one of the new Progressive Power Metal bands in Norway.
THeir music sounds a bit like Pagans Min and Circus Maximus.
They have released two demos wich can be bought:
1) On Sound of Noise, the best Metal store in Oslo,Norway
2: On the band&#039;s concerts
Or you can download them on the band&#039;s website: http://www.illusionsuite.net/

Enjoy !
